                     <interp inst="t18280410-226-person1276" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am watch-house-keeper of Kensington. I came home about half an hour after the prisoner was taken my wife gave me this carpet.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. There are a hundred carpets alike- I do not see how he can swear to it.</p>
